Release Notes for Version 3.13.0
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.13.0 is the 1st release in
the Errata Tool 3.13 development period. It closes [22 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release includes refinements to the [docker image support][dockerdocs]
released in version 3.12.5, improved support for end to end test advisories, a
fix for bugs with a large number of aliases, plus a number of other bug fixes
and enhancements.

